{"tid":1950496,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung Galaxy 集中討論區（77）點解咁快冇電","createTime":"2020-03-30T11:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T16:51:58.000Z","uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"345dfa115359e2a07d63d41ba02d19f159e3f28c","tid":1950496,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C5xCTmM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5xCTmM.gif&h=d945a69f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayNBPcy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FayNBPcy.png&h=3c03d1a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L69ea8C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL69ea8C.jpg&h=3db31e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受惠Snapdragon 865 性能提升，4K60都可以啟動影片穩定功能，附帶指紋解鎖速度亦有明顯提升。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKjpdMP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKjpdMP.gif&h=0824d46c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOne Ui 2.0<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNyMrg5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNyMrg5.gif&h=672f32c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WxjJcA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WxjJcA.gif&h=9b51556d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入手Galaxy S20 的建議：<br />\n120Hz+高性能模式+App Booster<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Labs已發布<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Labs是系統優化工具箱。<br />\n<br />\n這裡邊目前有四個組件：<br />\nBattery Guardian 自動優化、睡眠應用程序<br />\nBattery Tracker 跟踪app耗電量和時間<br />\nFile Guardian 可以恢復手機已刪除的文件<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">App Booster 提升App性能15%+5% 必裝！</span><br />\n(需直接down apk 因香港未推）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sammobile.com/news/samsung-galaxy-labs-suite-of-apps-let-you-optimize-your-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sammobile.com%2Fnews%2Fsamsung-galaxy-labs-suite-of-apps-let-you-optimize-your-phone%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2WmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=2d64691f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sammobile.com/news/samsung-galaxy-labs-suite-of-apps-let-you-optimize-your-phone/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y31Kc3C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy31Kc3C.jpg&h=5baf1b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手勢操作<br />\none hand operation<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tkVhuVX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtkVhuVX.jpg&h=e1fdfbb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.samsung.android.sidegesturepad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.samsung.android.sidegesturepad&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2WmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=f4a85f1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.samsung.android.sidegesturepad</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安全資料夾（勁有用）<br />\n<br />\n利用國防級的 Samsung Knox 安全平台，在您的三星手機上<span style=\"color: red;\">打造一個私人的加密空間</span>。移至安全資料夾的<span style=\"color: red;\">應用程序和數據</span>在設備中處於隔離的沙箱中，可獲得額外的安全性和私密性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n※ 安全資料夾是基於三星帳戶的服務，它可在您的移動設備中打造一個獨立的隔離環境。移動或添加至安全文件夾的應用程序和數據 (例如照片、音頻文件、電影文件和文檔) 將無法從安全文件夾外部訪問，無論是 USB 還是 Wi-Fi 直連都不可以。如果您的移動設備檢測到任何Root 權限獲取或ROM 自定義操作，為防止未授權的訪問，安全文件夾將自動鎖定，在這種情況下，您將無法再訪問或使用安全文件夾中的內容。因此，在將應用程序或數據移至安全文件夾之前，請務必在個人電腦等其他位置備份所有重要的應用程序或數據。<br />\n<br />\n安全資料夾操作邏輯<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dVPvSOleYxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdVPvSOleYxU&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2WmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=c1506d29\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dVPvSOleYxU</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\nSmart Octopus<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCAHotc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCAHotc.gif&h=0cd5fc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後360走了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWDVFJq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWDVFJq.png&h=9d1f42a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0crJ2i9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0crJ2i9.jpg&h=b7833550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>上面之前嘈緊360嘅<br />\nSamsung聽民意呀，踢走咗360啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/2020/02/05/samsung-device-care-360-integration/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidpolice.com%2F2020%2F02%2F05%2Fsamsung-device-care-360-integration%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2WmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=dd3a8f58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.androidpolice.com/2020/02/05/samsung-device-care-360-integration/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2k120hz缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n三星剛發布的S20 系列雖然配備了2K 屏和120Hz 刷新率，不過外媒評測證實這兩個選項並不能共存，只能1080P 120Hz 或2K 60Hz，<a href=\"http://於是有人跑去Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%96%BC%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%91%E5%8E%BBChange.org&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2WmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=7673d95b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">於是有人跑去Change.org</a>上發起請願要求開放2K +120hz。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbJ9pfu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbJ9pfu.jpg&h=19ec8519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/samsung-samsung-to-add-120hz-refresh-rate-wqhd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fsamsung-samsung-to-add-120hz-refresh-rate-wqhd&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2WmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=ef014aeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/samsung-samsung-to-add-120hz-refresh-rate-wqhd</a><br />\n<br />\nXDA Developers 網站的 Max Weinbach 昨日在 Twitter 爆料，表示 Samsung 正在為 Galaxy S20 系列的系統進行改善，包括將 120Hz 屏幕刷新率同時應用於 1440p 解像度，如果開發和測試過程順利的話，就會通過系統更新推送予所有 Galaxy S20 系列手機，預計在未來 1 至 3 個月會完成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-02/20/215252/uniqlo_1_81220ef7a2d2ca987ce7575f6ab11b7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-02%2F20%2F215252%2Funiqlo_1_81220ef7a2d2ca987ce7575f6ab11b7d.jpg&h=dd274ca5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3edadf6229cfc6c761ea12bd21631e321f744f6b","tid":1950496,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">完善系統體驗 X 120hz絕頂的流暢度</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相簿太多？<br />\n<br />\n為您的相簿分組  <br />\n將一個相簿拖入另一個相簿以將其合併為一個群組。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpbL8rV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpbL8rV.gif&h=0b334685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在一攝多拍中捕捉一切  <br />\n只需輕觸 [快門鍵]，相機即可自動決定拍攝對像與拍攝方式。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQD6STE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQD6STE.gif&h=75cadecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n絕不遺失一個標籤  <br />\n在瀏覽器應用程式中關閉標籤過早？透過選擇 [重新開啟已關閉的標籤] 立即重新將其開啟。您可多次選擇此選項以保持最近關閉的標籤開啟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jnA5o0w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjnA5o0w.gif&h=cc20adab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擷取整個螢幕  <br />\n擷取螢幕截圖後，輕觸 [捲動擷取] 按鍵以向下捲動螢幕並擷取更多。您甚至可以輕觸並按住 [捲動擷取] 按鍵以在一個長螢幕截圖中擷取整個螢幕或網頁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WK8yxTV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWK8yxTV.gif&h=eacd791e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手勢操作<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/22/091314_c96a00e85a9ec579b0ae284c6e606fef.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F091314_c96a00e85a9ec579b0ae284c6e606fef.gif&h=7e58f7da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滑動以復原或重做  <br />\n透過以兩指在鍵盤上向左滑動來復原您上次的編輯。以兩指向右滑動以重做編輯。<br />\n控制游標  <br />\n輕觸並按住空格鍵，然後向上或向下拖曳以控制游標。您還可使用多點觸控選擇文字。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3cO6d5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3cO6d5.gif&h=3d92792a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儲存網頁所有圖像  <br />\n儲存瀏覽器中目前網頁上的所有圖像。在下載中找到儲存的圖像。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xWT6SZt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxWT6SZt.gif&h=f344202f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剪貼板<br />\n不需再切換，一次過複製及貼上文字。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gi5hfeE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGi5hfeE.jpg&h=35417363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文字不能複製？ 文字提取功能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCYCfiu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCYCfiu.jpg&h=e086a798&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"596ebfdf594feb641307f93492972d81fdeed464","tid":1950496,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"點解係我踩中1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc113b897555e2517db84752c432cc3b05eea206","tid":1950496,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"究竟係我部機有問題定個個部ultra都係啲電去得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc0dd0adae732ce71d39469efe34be9daeff64b","tid":1950496,"uid":19892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:23:44.000Z","msg":"果邊爆左 過返黎問 s20+只可以入4個指紋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a3c6270d7f